## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full depth of the original theories proposed by Berger and Luckmann. Additionally, the interpretations of social constructionism can vary across different fields, leading to potential discrepancies in understanding. The report also does not cover all possible perspectives on the social construction of reality, focusing instead on the most widely recognized theories and concepts.

